library("tidyverse")
library("readxl")
library("tidycensus")
library("janitor")
library("sf")
library("leaflet")
library("urbnmapr")
library("tigris")
library("RSocrata")
library("tidylog")

Load Data

Click to show Code 
# Eviction data
evict_data_raw <- read.socrata(
  "https://data.cityofnewyork.us/resource/6z8x-wfk4.json")

evict_data <- evict_data_raw |> 
  mutate(year = as.numeric(substr(executed_date, 1, 4))) |> 
  filter(year >= 2022,
         !is.na(latitude),
         !is.na(longitude)) 
  

# Spatial data
nyc_counties_fips_list <- c("005", "047", "061", "081", "085")

tracts <- tracts(
  state = "NY",
  county = nyc_counties_fips_list,
  cb = TRUE,
  year = "2022"
  ) |> 
  janitor::clean_names() |> 
  st_transform(crs = 4326)

counties <- counties(
  state = "NY",
  cb = TRUE,
  year = "2022"
  ) |> 
  janitor::clean_names() |> 
  filter(countyfp %in% nyc_counties_fips_list) |> 
  st_transform(crs = 4326)

Lat & Long Map

Click to show Code 
# Convert evict_data df to sf 
evict_data_sf <- evict_data |> 
  st_as_sf(
    coords = c("longitude", "latitude"),
    crs = 4326)

# Leaflet map
leaflet() |> 
  # Basemap layer
  addProviderTiles(providers$CartoDB.Positron) |> 
  # County layer
  addPolygons(data = counties,
              fill = FALSE,
              stroke = TRUE,
              weight = 2,
              color = "black",
              opacity = 1,
              label = ~namelsad
              ) |> 
  # Tract layer 
  addPolygons(data = tracts,
              fillColor = "blue",
              color = "black",
              weight = 1,
              opacity = 0.5,
              fillOpacity = 0.3,
              label = ~tractce
              ) |> 
  # Add eviction points
  addCircleMarkers(data = evict_data_sf,
                   radius = 3,
                   color = "red",
                   label = ~marshal_last_name,
                   popup = ~paste("Name: ", marshal_last_name))

## Load Data
```{r}
#| output: false

# Eviction data
evict_data_raw <- read.socrata(
  "https://data.cityofnewyork.us/resource/6z8x-wfk4.json")

evict_data <- evict_data_raw |> 
  mutate(year = as.numeric(substr(executed_date, 1, 4))) |> 
  filter(year >= 2022,
         !is.na(latitude),
         !is.na(longitude)) 
  

# Spatial data
nyc_counties_fips_list <- c("005", "047", "061", "081", "085")

tracts <- tracts(
  state = "NY",
  county = nyc_counties_fips_list,
  cb = TRUE,
  year = "2022"
  ) |> 
  janitor::clean_names() |> 
  st_transform(crs = 4326)

counties <- counties(
  state = "NY",
  cb = TRUE,
  year = "2022"
  ) |> 
  janitor::clean_names() |> 
  filter(countyfp %in% nyc_counties_fips_list) |> 
  st_transform(crs = 4326)
```

## Lat & Long Map
```{r}
# Convert evict_data df to sf 
evict_data_sf <- evict_data |> 
  st_as_sf(
    coords = c("longitude", "latitude"),
    crs = 4326)

# Leaflet map
leaflet() |> 
  # Basemap layer
  addProviderTiles(providers$CartoDB.Positron) |> 
  # County layer
  addPolygons(data = counties,
              fill = FALSE,
              stroke = TRUE,
              weight = 2,
              color = "black",
              opacity = 1,
              label = ~namelsad
              ) |> 
  # Tract layer 
  addPolygons(data = tracts,
              fillColor = "blue",
              color = "black",
              weight = 1,
              opacity = 0.5,
              fillOpacity = 0.3,
              label = ~tractce
              ) |> 
  # Add eviction points
  addCircleMarkers(data = evict_data_sf,
                   radius = 3,
                   color = "red",
                   label = ~marshal_last_name,
                   popup = ~paste("Name: ", marshal_last_name))
  
```
